author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, Donald Trump has taken a major step towards fully abolishing the Department of Education. By every metric, the department has utterly failed our children. We’ll take a look at some of those metrics today. Also, alleged comedian Bill Burr appears on The View and has a nice polite conversation, making it one of the most disgraceful performances by a comedian of all time. A new video shows that we are very rapidly approaching the point where some crazed leftist is going to kill someone for driving a Tesla. And DoorDash will now offer you the chance to finance your Chipotle order.
